channel.title: [317] ~ Rune Imune ~ Server and Client Release
channel.description:
[center][IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/qoccbn.jpg[/img] [b]Getting Started:[/b] Hello everyone I'm Da 0wnz (previous producer of Lava Burn Isle) and this is my new server series called Rune-Imune. This server used to be hosted but after a while I got tired of noobs getting on and asking for staff, so I quit hosting it and decided to release it as a source. Took quite a while to make so I hope that you enjoy it!
[b]Description:[/b] You spawn at castle wars arena and to teleport you may either choose the portals or you can use the emotion tabs for teleporting.
[b]Pictures:[/b] [IMG]http://i43.tinypic.com/ae3bs9.png[/img] HOME [IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/2wme7nq.png[/img] Veng [IMG]http://i44.tinypic.com/wrl6oo.png[/img] Skills2 [IMG]http://i43.tinypic.com/29z4qa9.png[/img] Fishing and Cooking [IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/303ian6.png[/img] Jad [IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/21nf595.png[/img] Cape Emotes [IMG]http://i43.tinypic.com/t01awx.png[/img] Client [IMG]http://i44.tinypic.com/1hxg1j.png[/img] Slayer [IMG]http://i44.tinypic.com/34q35op.png[/img] Shops [IMG]http://i43.tinypic.com/1zbdpib.png[/img] Skills [IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/fyjq5x.png[/img] Custom Items [IMG]http://i44.tinypic.com/14si70z.png[/img] Team PK [IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/2ufasmq.png[/img] GS Mini
[b]Download Link:[/b] Server: [url=http://www.megaupload.com/?d=Y8IVVWWL]http://www.megaupload.com/?d=Y8IVVWWL[/url] Client: [url=http://www.megaupload.com/?d=RACE66P2]http://www.megaupload.com/?d=RACE66P2[/url]
[b]Credits:[/b] Da 0wnz - 75% (doing some major editing to the server and client) Mod Haseeb - 10% (server base) Who ever made The Revolution N1 - 10% (client base) Model Makers - 5% (models they have made)
